body_html:
we have versioned docs. http://pytorch.org/docs/master/ is the master branch. If you click on the version number in that page, you get to a version selector:
http://pytorch.org/docs/versions.html

This lets you choose docs for 0.1.12: http://pytorch.org/docs/0.1.12/
